Hotel Tanishque was born in 2001 as a dream to bring authentic Maharashtrian flavors and warm hospitality to the heart of Igatpuri â with a premium Bar & Restaurant under open skies with the warmth of home cooking and the elegance of fine dining.

For over 24 years, our chefs have been slow-cooking recipes that honor tradition â from the iconic Mutton Matka Biryani sealed in clay to the rich, aromatic Handi gravies that simmer for hours.
